<style>h1 {font-size: 34px;}
h1.title {font-size: 38px;}
h2 {font-size: 30px;}
h3 {font-size: 24px;}
h4 {font-size: 18px;}
h5 {font-size: 16px;}
h6 {font-size: 12px;}
code {color: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);}
pre:not([class]) { background-color: white }</style>
<style type="text/css">.pagedtable {
overflow: auto;
padding-left: 8px;
padding-right: 8px;
}
.pagedtable-wrapper {
border: 1px solid #ccc;
border-radius: 4px;
margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.pagedtable table {
width: 100%;
max-width: 100%;
margin: 0;
}
.pagedtable th {
padding: 0 5px 0 5px;
border: none;
border-bottom: 2px solid #dddddd;
min-width: 45px;
}
.pagedtable-empty th {
display: none;
}
.pagedtable td {
padding: 0 4px 0 4px;
}
.pagedtable .even {
background-color: rgba(140, 140, 140, 0.1);
}
.pagedtable-padding-col {
display: none;
}
.pagedtable a {
-webkit-touch-callout: none;
-webkit-user-select: none;
-khtml-user-select: none;
-moz-user-select: none;
-ms-user-select: none;
user-select: none;
}
.pagedtable-index-nav {
cursor: pointer;
padding: 0 5px 0 5px;
float: right;
border: 0;
}
.pagedtable-index-nav-disabled {
cursor: default;
text-decoration: none;
color: #999;
}
a.pagedtable-index-nav-disabled:hover {
text-decoration: none;
color: #999;
}
.pagedtable-indexes {
cursor: pointer;
float: right;
border: 0;
}
.pagedtable-index-current {
cursor: default;
text-decoration: none;
font-weight: bold;
color: #333;
border: 0;
}
a.pagedtable-index-current:hover {
text-decoration: none;
font-weight: bold;
color: #333;
}
.pagedtable-index {
width: 30px;
display: inline-block;
text-align: center;
border: 0;
}
.pagedtable-index-separator-left {
display: inline-block;
color: #333;
font-size: 9px;
padding: 0 0 0 0;
cursor: default;
}
.pagedtable-index-separator-right {
display: inline-block;
color: #333;
font-size: 9px;
padding: 0 4px 0 0;
cursor: default;
}
.pagedtable-footer {
padding-top: 4px;
padding-bottom: 5px;
}
.pagedtable-not-empty .pagedtable-footer {
border-top: 2px solid #dddddd;
}
.pagedtable-info {
overflow: hidden;
color: #999;
white-space: nowrap;
text-overflow: ellipsis;
}
.pagedtable-header-name {
overflow: hidden;
text-overflow: ellipsis;
}
.pagedtable-header-type {
color: #999;
font-weight: 400;
}
.pagedtable-na-cell {
font-style: italic;
opacity: 0.3;
}
</style>

        (!me.fixedHeight() && resizeNewHeight !== resizeLastHeight)
      ) {
        resizeLastWidth = resizeNewWidth;
        resizeLastHeight = resizeNewHeight;

        setTimeout(resizeDelayed, 200);
        resizePending = true;
      } else {
        me.render();
        triggerOnChange();

        resizeLastWidth = -1;
        resizeLastHeight = -1;
      }
    }

    resizeNewWidth = newWidth;
    resizeNewHeight = newHeight;

    if (!resizePending) resizeDelayed();
  };
};

<script>

/**
 * jQuery Plugin: Sticky Tabs
 *
 * @author Aidan Lister <aidan@php.net>
 * adapted by Ruben Arslan to activate parent tabs too
 * http://www.aidanlister.com/2014/03/persisting-the-tab-state-in-bootstrap/
 */
(function($) {
  "use strict";
  $.fn.rmarkdownStickyTabs = function() {
    var context = this;
    // Show the tab corresponding with the hash in the URL, or the first tab
    var showStuffFromHash = function() {
      var hash = window.location.hash;
      var selector = hash ? 'a[href="' + hash + '"]' : 'li.active > a';
      var $selector = $(selector, context);
      if($selector.data('toggle') === "tab") {
        $selector.tab('show');
        // walk up the ancestors of this element, show any hidden tabs
        $selector.parents('.section.tabset').each(function(i, elm) {
          var link = $('a[href="#' + $(elm).attr('id') + '"]');
          if(link.data('toggle') === "tab") {
            link.tab("show");
          }
        });
      }
    };


    // Set the correct tab when the page loads
    showStuffFromHash(context);

    // Set the correct tab when a user uses their back/forward button
    $(window).on('hashchange', function() {
      showStuffFromHash(context);
    });

    // Change the URL when tabs are clicked
    $('a', context).on('click', function(e) {
      history.pushState(null, null, this.href);
      showStuffFromHash(context);
    });

    return this;
  };
}(jQuery));

window.buildTabsets = function(tocID) {

  // build a tabset from a section div with the .tabset class
  function buildTabset(tabset) {

    // check for fade and pills options
    var fade = tabset.hasClass("tabset-fade");
    var pills = tabset.hasClass("tabset-pills");
    var navClass = pills ? "nav-pills" : "nav-tabs";

    // determine the heading level of the tabset and tabs
    var match = tabset.attr('class').match(/level(\d) /);
    if (match === null)
      return;
    var tabsetLevel = Number(match[1]);
    var tabLevel = tabsetLevel + 1;

    // find all subheadings immediately below
    var tabs = tabset.find("div.section.level" + tabLevel);
    if (!tabs.length)
      return;

    // create tablist and tab-content elements
    var tabList = $('<ul class="nav ' + navClass + '" role="tablist"></ul>');
    $(tabs[0]).before(tabList);
    var tabContent = $('<div class="tab-content"></div>');
    $(tabs[0]).before(tabContent);

    // build the tabset
    var activeTab = 0;
    tabs.each(function(i) {

      // get the tab div
      var tab = $(tabs[i]);

      // get the id then sanitize it for use with bootstrap tabs
      var id = tab.attr('id');

      // see if this is marked as the active tab
      if (tab.hasClass('active'))
        activeTab = i;

      // remove any table of contents entries associated with
      // this ID (since we'll be removing the heading element)
      $("div#" + tocID + " li a[href='#" + id + "']").parent().remove();

      // sanitize the id for use with bootstrap tabs
      id = id.replace(/[.\/?&!#<>]/g, '').replace(/\s/g, '_');
      tab.attr('id', id);

      // get the heading element within it, grab it's text, then remove it
      var heading = tab.find('h' + tabLevel + ':first');
      var headingText = heading.html();
      heading.remove();

      // build and append the tab list item
      var a = $('<a role="tab" data-toggle="tab">' + headingText + '</a>');
      a.attr('href', '#' + id);
      a.attr('aria-controls', id);
      var li = $('<li role="presentation"></li>');
      li.append(a);
      tabList.append(li);

      // set it's attributes
      tab.attr('role', 'tabpanel');
      tab.addClass('tab-pane');
      tab.addClass('tabbed-pane');
      if (fade)
        tab.addClass('fade');

      // move it into the tab content div
      tab.detach().appendTo(tabContent);
    });

    // set active tab
    $(tabList.children('li')[activeTab]).addClass('active');
    var active = $(tabContent.children('div.section')[activeTab]);
    active.addClass('active');
    if (fade)
      active.addClass('in');

    if (tabset.hasClass("tabset-sticky"))
      tabset.rmarkdownStickyTabs();
  }

  // convert section divs with the .tabset class to tabsets
  var tabsets = $("div.section.tabset");
  tabsets.each(function(i) {
    buildTabset($(tabsets[i]));
  });
};

</script>

window.initializeCodeFolding = function(show) {

  // handlers for show-all and hide all
  $("#rmd-show-all-code").click(function() {
    $('div.r-code-collapse').each(function() {
      $(this).collapse('show');
    });
  });
  $("#rmd-hide-all-code").click(function() {
    $('div.r-code-collapse').each(function() {
      $(this).collapse('hide');
    });
  });

  // index for unique code element ids
  var currentIndex = 1;

  // select all R code blocks
  var rCodeBlocks = $('pre.r, pre.python, pre.bash, pre.sql, pre.cpp, pre.stan, pre.julia, pre.foldable');
  rCodeBlocks.each(function() {
    // skip if the block has fold-none class
    if ($(this).hasClass('fold-none')) return;

    // create a collapsable div to wrap the code in
    var div = $('<div class="collapse r-code-collapse"></div>');
    var showThis = (show || $(this).hasClass('fold-show')) && !$(this).hasClass('fold-hide');
    var id = 'rcode-643E0F36' + currentIndex++;
    div.attr('id', id);
    $(this).before(div);
    $(this).detach().appendTo(div);

    // add a show code button right above
    var showCodeText = $('<span>' + (showThis ? 'Hide' : 'Code') + '</span>');
    var showCodeButton = $('<button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-xs btn-secondary btn-sm code-folding-btn pull-right float-right"></button>');
    showCodeButton.append(showCodeText);
    showCodeButton
        .attr('data-toggle', 'collapse')
        .attr('data-bs-toggle', 'collapse') // BS5
        .attr('data-target', '#' + id)
        .attr('data-bs-target', '#' + id)   // BS5
        .attr('aria-expanded', showThis)
        .attr('aria-controls', id);

    var buttonRow = $('<div class="row"></div>');
    var buttonCol = $('<div class="col-md-12"></div>');

    buttonCol.append(showCodeButton);
    buttonRow.append(buttonCol);

    div.before(buttonRow);

    // show the div if necessary
    if (showThis) div.collapse('show');

    // update state of button on show/hide
    //   * Change text
    //   * add a class for intermediate states styling
    div.on('hide.bs.collapse', function () {
      showCodeText.text('Code');
      showCodeButton.addClass('btn-collapsing');
    });
    div.on('hidden.bs.collapse', function () {
      showCodeButton.removeClass('btn-collapsing');
    });
    div.on('show.bs.collapse', function () {
      showCodeText.text('Hide');
      showCodeButton.addClass('btn-expanding');
    });
    div.on('shown.bs.collapse', function () {
      showCodeButton.removeClass('btn-expanding');
    });

  });

}
</script>

<div id="question-1" class="section level2">
<h2>Question 1</h2>
<p>Dalam studi kualitas air di sungai di Selandia Baru, yang
didokumentasikan dalam McBride dkk. (2002), Campylobacter level tinggi
didefinisikan sebagai level yang lebih besar dari 100 per 100 ml air
sungai. Sebanyak <span class="math inline">\(n = 116\)</span> sampel
diambil dari sungai yang memiliki dampak lingkungan level tinggi dari
burung. Dari jumlah tersebut, <span class="math inline">\(y =
11\)</span> memiliki tingkat Campylobacter yang tinggi. Misalkan <span class="math inline">\(\pi\)</span> adalah nilai peluang yang sebenarnya
bahwa sampel air dari jenis sungai ini memiliki tingkat Campylobacter
yang tinggi.</p>
<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha">
<li>Hitunglah penduga frequentist untuk <span class="math inline">\(\pi\)</span>.</li>
<li>Gunakan prior Beta<span class="math inline">\((1, 10)\)</span> untuk
<span class="math inline">\(\pi\)</span>. Hitung distribusi posterior
<span class="math inline">\(g(\pi|y)\)</span>.</li>
<li>Hitunglah mean dan ragam posterior. Apa yang dimaksud dengan penduga
Bayesian untuk <span class="math inline">\(\pi\)</span>?</li>
<li>Tentukan credible interval sebesar 95% untuk <span class="math inline">\(\pi\)</span>.</li>
<li>Uji hipotesis <span class="math display">\[
H_0 : \pi=0.10 \ \ \text{vs} \ \ H_{1}: \pi \neq 0.10
\]</span></li>
</ol>
</div>
<div id="answer-1" class="section level2">
<h2>Answer 1</h2>
<p>Masalah ini dapat didekati dengan sebaran binomial dengan kejadian
sukses adalah Campylobacter level tinggi dan kejadian tidak sukses
adalah Campylobacter level tidak tinggi.</p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
p_{Y}(y) = {n \choose k}\pi^y (1-\pi)^{n-y}
\]</span></p>
<div id="a-hitunglah-penduga-frequentist-untuk-pi." class="section level3">
<h3>(a) Hitunglah penduga frequentist untuk <span class="math inline">\(\pi\)</span>.</h3>
<p>Metode frequentist untuk mendapatkan penduga paramater antara lain
dengan MLE(Maximum Likelihood Estimation)</p>
<p>fungsi likelihood dari binomial</p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
L(\pi|\mathbf{y}) = \prod_{i=1}^{n} \binom{n}{x_i}
\pi^{x_i}(1-\pi)^{n-x_i}
\]</span></p>
<p>fungsi log-likelihood dari binomial</p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\ell(p) = \log \mathcal{L}(p) = \sum_{i=1}^n \log \binom{n}{y_i} + y_i
\log \pi + (n-y_i)\log(1-\pi)
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\frac{d}{dp}\log \mathcal{L}(p)= \frac{d}{d\pi}\left[\sum_{i=1}^n
\left(\log \binom{n}{y_i} + y_i \log \pi + (n-y_i)\log(1-\pi))\right)
\right] = 0
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\begin{aligned}
\sum_{i=1}^n 0 + \sum_{i=1}{\frac{y_i}{\pi}} +
\sum_{i=1}-\frac{(n-y_i)}{(1-\pi)}&amp;=0 \\
\sum_{i=1}{\frac{y_i}{\pi}} &amp;=\sum_{i=1}\frac{(n-y_i)}{(1-\pi)} \\
\sum_{i=1}{\frac{1-\pi}{\pi}} &amp;= \sum_{i=1}\frac{(n-y_i)}{y_i} \\
\sum_{i=1}{\frac{1}{\pi}-1} &amp;= \sum_{i=1}\frac{n}{y_i}-1 \\
p &amp;= \sum_{i=1}\frac{y_i}{n}
\end{aligned}
\]</span></p>
<p>Jadi berdasarkan metode frequentis didapatkan</p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\hat{\pi}=\sum_{i=1}\frac{y_i}{n}
\]</span> sehingga</p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\hat{\pi}=\sum_{i=1}\frac{y_i}{n}=\frac{11}{116}=0.09482759
\]</span></p>
</div>
<div id="b-gunakan-prior-beta1-10-untuk-pi.-hitung-distribusi-posterior-gpiy" class="section level3">
<h3>(b) Gunakan prior Beta<span class="math inline">\((1, 10)\)</span>
untuk <span class="math inline">\(\pi\)</span>. Hitung distribusi
posterior <span class="math inline">\(g(\pi|y)\)</span></h3>

<pre class="r"><code># data
data &lt;- list(n = 116, y = 11)

# model
model_string &lt;- 
&quot;
data {
  int&lt;lower=0&gt; n;
  int&lt;lower=0&gt; y;
}
parameters {
  real&lt;lower=0, upper=1&gt; pi;
}
model {
  pi ~ beta(1, 10);
  y ~ binomial(n, pi);
}
&quot;

# compile the model
model &lt;- stan_model(model_code = model_string)

# run the MCMC sampler
fit &lt;- sampling(model, data = data)</code></pre>

<p><span class="math display">\[
\pi = 0.09419489
\]</span></p>
<p>Cara lain:</p>
<p>karena distribusi beta merupakan conjugate prior bagi distribusi
binomial maka posterior yang dihasilkan adalah distribusi beta-binomial
atau <span class="math inline">\(\text{Beta}(\alpha+y,\beta+n-y)\)</span> atau
<span class="math inline">\(\text{Beta}(11+1,10+116-11)\)</span> atau
<span class="math inline">\(\text{Beta}(12,115)\)</span>. Sehingga kita
hanya perlu menghitung nilai ekspetasi dan variance dari peubah acak
yang menyebar <span class="math inline">\(\text{Beta}(12,115)\)</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\begin{aligned}
E(\pi|y)&amp;=\frac{\alpha}{\alpha+\beta} \\
&amp;= \frac{12}{127} \\
&amp;= 0.09448819
\end{aligned}
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\text{Var}(\pi|y)=\frac{\alpha+\beta}{(\alpha+\beta)^{2}(\alpha+\beta)}=\frac{127}{127^2
127} =  0.0006571973
\]</span></p>

<div id="e-uji-hipotesis" class="section level3">
<h3>(e) Uji hipotesis</h3>
<p><span class="math display">\[
H_0 : \pi=0.10 \ \ \text{vs} \ \ H_{1}: \pi \neq 0.10
\]</span></p>
<p>karena uji hipotesis diatas merupakan uji dua arah maka akan
digunakan credible interval, dengan memeriksa apakah <span class="math inline">\(\pi=0.10\)</span> berada di dalam atau diluar
kredible interval. Jika <span class="math inline">\(\pi=0.10\)</span>
berada di dalam interval maka <span class="math inline">\(H_0\)</span>
tidak ditolak. Jika <span class="math inline">\(\pi=0.10\)</span> berada
di luar interval maka <span class="math inline">\(H_0\)</span>
ditolak.</p>
<p>Berdasarkan hasil (d) credible intervalnya adalah <span class="math inline">\((0.05018522,0.15083792)\)</span> sehingga <span class="math inline">\(0.10 \in (0.05018522 ,0.15083792)\)</span> yang
berarti <span class="math inline">\(H_0\)</span> tidak ditolak.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="question-2" class="section level2">
<h2>Question 2</h2>
<p>Misalkan diketahui <span class="math inline">\(Y\)</span> menyebar
<span class="math inline">\(\text{Poisson}(\lambda)\)</span>. Jika
diketahui 5 nilai pengamatan bagi <span class="math inline">\(Y\)</span>
yaitu</p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
12, 17, 10, 8, 23
\]</span></p>
<p>Tentukan sebaran posterior dengan menggunakan metode MCMC dalam R,
kemudian dapatkan penduga <span class="math inline">\(\lambda\)</span>
dan 95% credible interval berdasarkan sebaran posterior jika</p>
<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha">
<li>sebaran prior <span class="math inline">\(\text{Gamma}(3,6)\)</span></li>
<li>sebaran prior <span class="math inline">\(\text{Log-normal}(2)\)</span></li>
<li>sebaran prior <span class="math inline">\(\text{Beta}(2,1)\)</span></li>
<li>sebaran prior Laplace’s prior yaitu:</li>
</ol>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\pi(\lambda)=\frac{1}{4} \exp\left(-\frac{|\lambda-3|)}{2}\right)
\]</span></p>
</div>
<div id="answer-2" class="section level2">
<h2>Answer 2</h2>
<div id="a.-sebaran-prior-textgamma36" class="section level3">
<h3>a. sebaran prior <span class="math inline">\(\text{Gamma}(3,6)\)</span></h3>
<!-- rnb-text-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->
<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxubGlicmFyeShyc3RhbilcbmxpYnJhcnkoZ2dwdWJyKVxubGlicmFyeShnZ3Bsb3QyKVxuYGBgIn0= -->
<pre class="r"><code>library(rstan)
library(ggpubr)
library(ggplot2)</code></pre>
<!-- rnb-source-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-end -->
<!-- rnb-text-begin -->
<!-- rnb-text-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->
<!-- rnb-source-begin  -->
<pre class="r"><code># data
y2 &lt;-  c(12, 17, 10, 8, 23)
n2 &lt;- length(y2)
data2 &lt;- list(n=n2,y=y2)


# model
model_string2 &lt;- 
&quot;
data {
  int n;          // banyaknya data
  int y[n];       // Data
}

parameters {
  real&lt;lower=0&gt; lambda;  // Parameter lambda
}

model {
  lambda ~ gamma(3, 6);  // Prior lambda
  y ~ poisson(lambda);   // Likelihood
}
&quot;

# compile the model
model2 &lt;- stan_model(model_code = model_string2)

# run the MCMC sampler
fit2 &lt;- sampling(model2, data = data2)</code></pre>

<div id="d.-sebaran-prior-laplaces-prior" class="section level3">
<h3>d. sebaran prior Laplace’s prior</h3>
<p>secara umum Laplace’s prior memiliki nama lain sebaran yaitu
double-exponential. Silahkan lihat lebih lanjut di</p>
<p><a href="https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Laplace_distribution" class="uri">https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Laplace_distribution</a></p>
<!-- rnb-text-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->
<!-- rnb-source-begin  -->
<pre class="r"><code># data
y2 &lt;-  c(12, 17, 10, 8, 23)
n2 &lt;- length(y2)
data2 &lt;- list(n=n2,y=y2)


# model
model_string2d &lt;- 
&quot;
data {
  int n;          // Banyaknya data
  int y[n];       // Data

}

parameters {
  real&lt;lower=0&gt; lambda;  // Parameter lambda
}

model {
  lambda ~ double_exponential(3, 2);  // Prior lambda
  y ~ poisson(lambda);       // Likelihood
}
&quot;

# compile the model
model2d &lt;- stan_model(model_code = model_string2d)

# run the MCMC sampler
fit2d &lt;- sampling(model2d, data = data2)</code></pre>

<div id="question-3" class="section level2">
<h2>Question 3</h2>
<p>Seorang statistisi bertanggung jawab atas standar kualitas di pabrik
keju. Statistisi itu ingin menghitung peluang bahwa blok keju yang
dipilih secara acak dari blok berlabel “1 kg” yang sebenarnya kurang
dari 1 kilogram (1.000 gram) adalah 1% atau kurang. Berat (dalam gram)
blok keju yang diproduksi oleh mesin menyebar <span class="math inline">\(\text{Normal}(\mu,3^2)\)</span> normal. Diketahui
Berat (dalam gram) dari 20 blok keju adalah</p>
<!-- rnb-text-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->
<!-- rnb-frame-begin  -->
<div data-pagedtable="false">
<script data-pagedtable-source type="application/json">
{"columns":[{"label":["blok1"],"name":[1],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok2"],"name":[2],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok3"],"name":[3],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok4"],"name":[4],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok5"],"name":[5],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok6"],"name":[6],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok7"],"name":[7],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok8"],"name":[8],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok9"],"name":[9],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok10"],"name":[10],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok11"],"name":[11],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok12"],"name":[12],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok13"],"name":[13],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok14"],"name":[14],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok15"],"name":[15],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok16"],"name":[16],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok17"],"name":[17],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok18"],"name":[18],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok19"],"name":[19],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]},{"label":["blok20"],"name":[20],"type":["dbl"],"align":["right"]}],"data":[{"1":"994","2":"997","3":"999","4":"1003","5":"994","6":"998","7":"1001","8":"998","9":"996","10":"1002","11":"1004","12":"995","13":"994","14":"995","15":"998","16":"1001","17":"995","18":"1006","19":"997","20":"998"}],"options":{"columns":{"min":{},"max":[10],"total":[20]},"rows":{"min":[10],"max":[10],"total":[1]},"pages":{}}}
  </script>
</div>
<!-- rnb-frame-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-end -->
<!-- rnb-text-begin -->
<p>Statistisi tersebut berasumsi prior untuk <span class="math inline">\(\mu\)</span> memiliki sebaran <span class="math inline">\(\text{Normal}(1000,10)\)</span>. Dengan
menggunakan metode MCMC dalam R hitunglah</p>
<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha">
<li>sebaran posterior dari <span class="math inline">\(\mu\)</span></li>
<li>peluang posterior bahwa <span class="math inline">\(\mu&lt;1000\)</span></li>
<li>apakah mesin tersebut tersebut perlu dikalibrasi?</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div id="answer-3" class="section level2">
<h2>Answer 3</h2>
<div id="a.-sebaran-posterior-dari-mu" class="section level3">
<h3>a. sebaran posterior dari <span class="math inline">\(\mu\)</span></h3>
<!-- rnb-text-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->
<!-- rnb-source-begin  -->
<pre class="r"><code># data
y3 &lt;-  c(994,997,999,1003,994,998,1001,998,996,1002,1004, 995, 994, 995, 998, 1001, 995, 1006, 997, 998)
n3 &lt;- length(y3)
data3 &lt;- list(n=n3,y=y3)


# model
model_string3 &lt;- 
&quot;
data {
  int n;          // Banyaknya data
  real y[n];       // Data

}

parameters {
  real mu;  // Parameter mu
}

model {
  mu ~ normal(1000, 10);  // Prior mu
  y ~ normal(mu,3);       // Likelihood
}
&quot;

# compile the model
model3 &lt;- stan_model(model_code = model_string3)

# run the MCMC sampler
fit3 &lt;- sampling(model3, data = data3)</code></pre>

<div id="question-4" class="section level2">
<h2>Question 4</h2>
<p>Kelompok pengawas konsumen lokal prihatin dengan biaya listrik yang
dibebankan kepada pelanggan rumah tangga selama bulan-bulan musim dingin
di New Zealand (Southern Hemisphere). Mereka mengambil data dari 25 akun
listrik perumahan dan melihat total biaya listrik yang digunakan selama
tiga bulan, yaitu Juni, Juli, dan Agustus. Biaya listrik yang
dikeluarkan adalah sebagai berikut:</p>
<!-- rnb-text-end -->

<p>Asumsikan bahwa Biaya listrik yang dikeluarkan selama tiga bulan oleh
suatu akun perumahan adalah <span class="math inline">\(\text{Normal}(\mu; \sigma^2)\)</span>, dengan
simpangan baku yang diketahui <span class="math inline">\(\sigma^2=
80\)</span>.</p>
<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha">
<li>Gunakan prior <span class="math inline">\(\text{Normal}(325;
80^2)\)</span> untuk <span class="math inline">\(\mu\)</span>. Hitung
posterior untuk dengan MCMC pada R.</li>
<li>Hitunglah 95% credible interval untuk <span class="math inline">\(\mu\)</span></li>
<li>Lakukan pengujian hipotesis dengan level 5% untuk hipotesis berikut
ini:</li>
</ol>
<p><span class="math display">\[
H_{0}:\mu=350 \ \text{vs} \ H_{1}:\mu\neq 350
\]</span></p>

<div id="answer-4" class="section level2">
<h2>Answer 4</h2>
<div id="a.-gunakan-prior-textnormal325-802-untuk-mu.-hitung-posterior-untuk-dengan-mcmc-pada-r." class="section level3">
<h3>a. Gunakan prior <span class="math inline">\(\text{Normal}(325;
80^2)\)</span> untuk <span class="math inline">\(\mu\)</span>. Hitung
posterior untuk dengan MCMC pada R.</h3>
<p>grafik prior</p>
<!-- rnb-text-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->
<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxuc2ViYXJhbl9wcmlvciA8LSBybm9ybSgxMDAwLG1lYW4gPSAzMjUsc2QgPSA4MClcbmdnZGVuc2l0eShkYXRhID0gZGF0YS5mcmFtZShwb3N0ZXJpb3I9c2ViYXJhbl9wcmlvciksXG4gICAgICAgICAgeD1cInBvc3RlcmlvclwiLGZpbGw9XCJzdGVlbGJsdWVcIikrXG4gIHNjYWxlX3lfY29udGludW91cyhleHBhbmQgPSBjKDAsMCkpXG5gYGAifQ== -->
<pre class="r"><code>sebaran_prior &lt;- rnorm(1000,mean = 325,sd = 80)
ggdensity(data = data.frame(posterior=sebaran_prior),

  scale_y_continuous(expand = c(0,0))</code></pre>
<!-- rnb-source-end -->

<pre class="r"><code># data
y4 &lt;-  c(514, 536,345,440,427,443,386,418,364,483,506, 385, 410, 561, 275,
306, 294, 402, 350, 343,480, 334, 324, 414, 296)
n4 &lt;- length(y4)
data4 &lt;- list(n=n4,y=y4)


# model
model_string4 &lt;- 
&quot;
data {
  int n;          // Banyaknya data
  real y[n];       // Data

}

parameters {
  real mu;  // Parameter mu
}

model {
  mu ~ normal(1000, 80);  // Prior mu
  y ~ normal(mu,80);       // Likelihood
}
&quot;

# compile the model
model4 &lt;- stan_model(model_code = model_string4)

# run the MCMC sampler
fit4 &lt;- sampling(model4, data = data4)</code></pre>

<div id="c.-lakukan-pengujian-hipotesis-dengan-level-5-untuk-hipotesis-berikut-ini" class="section level3">
<h3>c. Lakukan pengujian hipotesis dengan level 5% untuk hipotesis
berikut ini:</h3>
<p><span class="math display">\[
H_{0}:\mu=350 \ \text{vs} \ H_{1}:\mu\neq 350
\]</span></p>
<p>karena uji hipotesis diatas merupakan uji dua arah maka akan
digunakan credible interval, dengan memeriksa apakah <span class="math inline">\(\mu=350\)</span> berada di dalam atau diluar
credible interval. Jika <span class="math inline">\(\mu=350\)</span>
berada di dalam interval maka <span class="math inline">\(H_0\)</span>
tidak ditolak. Jika <span class="math inline">\(\mu=350\)</span> berada
di luar interval maka <span class="math inline">\(H_0\)</span>
ditolak.</p>
<p>Berdasarkan hasil (b) credible intervalnya adalah <span class="math inline">\((393.3456,456.6803)\)</span> sehingga <span class="math inline">\(350 \notin (393.3456,456.6803)\)</span> yang
berarti <span class="math inline">\(H_0\)</span> ditolak.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="b.-hitung-penduga-koefisien-berdasarkan-konsep-bayesian-dengan-menggunakan-mcmc-dalam-r." class="section level3">
<h3>b. Hitung penduga koefisien berdasarkan konsep bayesian dengan
menggunakan MCMC dalam R.</h3>
<p>karena tidak ada informasi tentang prior kita bisa menggunakan flat
prior</p>
<p>dengan sebaran uniform</p>
<!-- rnb-text-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->
<!-- rnb-source-begin  -->
<pre class="r"><code># data
n5 &lt;- nrow(data5)
stan_data &lt;- list(n=n5,y=data5$hasil_panen,x=data5$tingkat_pemupukan)


# model
model_string5 &lt;- 
&quot;
data {
  int n;          // Banyaknya data
  vector[n] x;  
  vector[n] y;    

}

parameters {
real beta0;
real beta1;
real&lt;lower=0&gt; sigma;
}

model {
beta0 ~ uniform(0,100);
beta1 ~ uniform(0,100);
sigma ~ uniform(0,10);
y ~ normal(beta0 + beta1 * x, sigma);
}
&quot;

# compile the model
model5 &lt;- stan_model(model_code = model_string5)

# run the MCMC sampler
fit5 &lt;- sampling(model5, data = stan_data)</code></pre>
<!-- rnb-source-end -->
<!-- rnb-output-begin  -->
<pre><code>
